 arch/arm/boot/dts/overlays/Makefile           |  1 +
 arch/arm/boot/dts/overlays/README             | 21 +++++++++++++++++++
 .../dts/overlays/rpi-poe-plus-overlay.dts     | 19 +++++++++++++++++
